    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >历史上最强英雄，拯救人类最离谱的危机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时间线陷落了。蜥蜴人势力撕裂时空屏障，带来了恐龙机械兵、激光迅猛龙，甚至还有最可怕的敌人——独裁龙。这一次，必须由人类历史中最传奇的英雄们组成梦之队，力挽狂澜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Reptilian Rising》是一款致敬80年代桌游风格的回合制策略RPG。指挥你的复古微缩模型小队，穿梭在从原始时代到未来战场的各个时空。组建团队、强化能力，甚至弯曲时间来逆转战局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>小队战术，复古风范</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗采用快节奏、带有“反应机制”的回合制战斗系统。每次攻击都会引发敌人的即时回应。嗨，你明白吧？你得深思熟虑、连锁技能、利用地形优势。战场布局随机、难度逐步升级，每一局都是全新挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625460/extras/9d185180b67492cedf9fe92c65a88625.poster.avif?t=1772205187\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625460/extras/9d185180b67492cedf9fe92c65a88625.webm?t=1772205187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625460/extras/9d185180b67492cedf9fe92c65a88625.mp4?t=1772205187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>反派角色，但要搞怪</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这可不是一般的蜥蜴人入侵。迎战邪恶机械蜥人、致命激光迅猛龙，还有三个脑袋都火力全开的三连炮龙。以及可怕的终极对手——独裁龙。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >祝你好运，朋友。你肯定需要这个诚挚的祝福的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625460/extras/21c6008fcbc0dab823601bb86a01d9fb.poster.avif?t=1772205187\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625460/extras/21c6008fcbc0dab823601bb86a01d9fb.webm?t=1772205187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625460/extras/21c6008fcbc0dab823601bb86a01d9fb.mp4?t=1772205187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>大坏蛋vs大人物</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当三个臭名昭著的大反派共用一具恐龙巨躯，你就得召唤出我们人类历史上最厉害的大人物来奋起反击。从凯撒大帝到中世纪神射手罗宾汉，再到超级科学天才爱因斯坦。万物皆相对，但我们绝对要痛击蜥蜴人！一起来参加这场跨越时空的超级大乱斗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625460/extras/be59a1a3c2ff0cc41c291a5200356b89.poster.avif?t=1772205187\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625460/extras/be59a1a3c2ff0cc41c291a5200356b89.webm?t=1772205187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625460/extras/be59a1a3c2ff0cc41c291a5200356b89.mp4?t=1772205187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>时间混战，脑洞全开</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越时空可远不止跳进德罗宁跑车、钻进电话亭或复古警亭那么简单。在《Reptilian Rising》中你将运用时间能量施展战术，让爬虫族措手不及。复制部队、召唤跨时代援军（我们真的有刀疤脸的电话号码），或开启时间之门让英雄们以双倍速度横跨战场！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625460/extras/3fd1064347a4f954427faadfe3f629c0.poster.avif?t=1772205187\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625460/extras/3fd1064347a4f954427faadfe3f629c0.webm?t=1772205187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625460/extras/3fd1064347a4f954427faadfe3f629c0.mp4?t=1772205187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>循环中的秘密</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只要你能逆转时空而不引发时间悖论，你就可以反复挑战任务，完成额外目标，在不同时代间穿梭探索隐藏秘密，还有更多惊喜等你发现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625460/extras/13e40c3c7f7922a3453f175c9148d6a4.poster.avif?t=1772205187\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625460/extras/13e40c3c7f7922a3453f175c9148d6a4.webm?t=1772205187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625460/extras/13e40c3c7f7922a3453f175c9148d6a4.mp4?t=1772205187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Reptilian Rising》将于2026年正式发售。现在就加入愿望单，装弹、上膛、穿越时空！听我口令——开门，卧倒，瞄准恐龙全力开火吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625460/extras/bf780550461c643786666ddea62eddb8.poster.avif?t=1772205187\" width=1170 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625460/extras/bf780550461c643786666ddea62eddb8.webm?t=1772205187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1625460/extras/bf780550461c643786666ddea62eddb8.mp4?t=1772205187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >回合制小队战术，搭配反应机制带来新鲜战斗体验</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20+来自历史、神话与脑洞宇宙的传奇英雄</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数十种离谱敌人与 9 场风格各异的 Boss 战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包含神器、克隆、时间之门等在内的策略升级系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高重玩性，任务分支与挑战目标助你解锁更多秘密</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独具特色的 80 年代桌游视觉风格，重现经典时代魅力</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
